smallsrv (3.06.35test13) unstable; urgency=low

  * Changed loading/saving configuration. Added support for comments
  * Fixed editing configuration from the web interface
  * A little fix in VPN
  * A little but importen fix in HTTP, and loging
  * Fixed web mail
  * Fixed issue when MD5 Digest authentication unavilable for user,
    because password crypted
  * Added checking each variable from language support file for compatible
  * Added a separate VPN client application
  * Some changes in source organisation

