  * Fixed bug in CGI

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Sat, 13 Jul 2024 08:31:16 +0400

smallsrv (3.06.31) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added support for trafic limitation to VPN server.
  * Changed incoming/outgoing counters to 64bits .
  * In the security libraries support files changed max version
    to TLS 1.2 by default
    When max version is TLS 1.3 Android API client can't handshake.
  * Fixed config param VPN DNS
  * Fixed TLS SetPriority for binary with pre-builded security library
  * Added support for DNS-based Named Entity Authentication (DANE)
    (RFC6698) to the DNS server.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:33:41 +0400

