  * For Linux added system user/password authorization support.
  * Enabled paterns for users name for private virtual directories.
  * Added detection of DoS attacks when there are a large number
    of slow connections.
  * Fixed SMTP client (EHLO after STARTTLS).
  * Fixed DNS log.
  * Added man
  * Optimised AddToLogDNS.
  * Function MyLock updated.
  * Little changes.

