smallsrv (3.05.61) unstable; urgency=low

  * In SMTP server send outside algoritm changed.
  * Proxy changed. Option for no cashe pages when request content
    cookes has been added.
  * Little change in CGI execution.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Tue, 07 Nov 2006 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (3.05.60) unstable; urgency=low

  * Now the program can show statistic by countries and server may add
    REMOTE_COUNTRY variably with country name to SSI/CGI enviroment.
    IP-contry database need for these features. Database is compresed
    (about 130Kb file and allocate about 300 Kb in memory). Fast search
    will not delay SSI and CGI execution. The program does not garanted
    valid country detection for evry time, but in many times it will be.
    For IP addresses that absent in database the server show "unknown"
    instead country name. Now the country database does not content some
    IP of USA and Canada because AIRN doesn't public full IP database.
    (Or I doesn't found it. If somebody know where is full AIRN database
    avilable, please let me know)
  * Another little changes in HTTP,FTP,SMTP,DNS.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Wed, 27 Sep 2006 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (3.05.59) unstable; urgency=low

  * Now in DNSBL (external blackhole lists) you may direct more then
    one servers through space
  * Some mistake in version 3.05.57 has been fixed.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Mon, 11 Sep 2006 00:00:00 +0300

