smallsrv (3.03962) unstable; urgency=low

  * SSI was updated, some mistakes was revised.
  * Statistics for POP3 and HTTP has been appended.
  * The possibility of using up level proxy server has been added.
  * Now IP range for which the servers are avilable can be multiple.

  * Web Mail was updated Get 1.12 (25Kb)
Work with external POP3 servers has been optimised. Keys for
  administrator to run with shedule auto checking new mail on external
  POP3 servers by users orders, has been added.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Sun, 27 Oct 2002 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (3.0395) unstable; urgency=low

  * Statistics for mail has been appended.
  * Proxy was updated.
  * Some bugs fixed.
  * Now server detects the trying to catch the password, and doesn't
    receive next requests from hacker's hosts.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Sat, 05 Oct 2002 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (3.0392) unstable; urgency=low

  * unstable for Linux
  * It's nearly simelar with 3.0392 for Windows, but it has some
    differents that are specific for UNIX.
    - E.g. CGI ident isn't used, the files that have "executable for
      other" mode attribute are files to run.
    - If server has a right to change current user, the scripts will be
      run from user's id of the file.
    - The files that have "readable for other" mode attribute are files
      to return.
    - FTP support SITE command.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Sun, 22 Sep 2002 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (3.0391) unstable; urgency=low

  * Autorization for proxy
  * Error file
  * Interface to NT Service updated.
  * Optimized.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Sat, 14 Sep 2002 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (3.039) unstable; urgency=low

  * The support of virtual directory (common directory for all hosts)
    has been added
  * Now server can run as NT servise.
  * Changes in HTTP and Proxy, persistent connections.
  * DNS over TCP, support AXFR requests
  * Statistics for DNS hosts.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Wed, 24 Jul 2002 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (3.038) unstable; urgency=low

  * DNS server is updated. Reqursion and cache have been added.
  * Optional conversion names with space in FTP.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Wed, 05 Jun 2002 00:00:00 +0300

