smallsrv (3.035) unstable; urgency=low

  * Limitatition of SMTP message size.
  * Now server creates as much threads as realy nessesary.
  * SMTP server is updated. Now you can optional enable to send message
    from any address. Also you can restrict IP range, that enable to send
    message via your SMTP.
  * Server correct works with file names that content space.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Fri, 07 Dec 2001 00:00:00 +0300

