 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Sat, 22 Jan 2000 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (1.209) unstable; urgency=low

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Sat, 15 Jan 2000 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (1.208) experimental; urgency=medium

  * Multihosting support has been added.
    - Now you can create some different host names in your PC, link any
      name with own web root directory.
  * Now any web directory could have own cgi-bin subdir.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Fri, 17 Dec 1999 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (1.207) unstable; urgency=low

  * In SSI-tag if "part of ..." logic operation has been added:
    - "str1 ~ str2" -- the result is true, if the string str2 is the
      part of string str1 E.g.:
    - <!--#if expr="$USER_AGENT ~ Win95" -->  Text for '95 users only
      ... <!--#endif -->

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Fri, 10 Dec 1999 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (1.206) unstable; urgency=low

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Wed, 08 Dec 1999 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (1.206b) experimental; urgency=medium

  * Resuming.
  * Method HEAD.
  * Now, if the file name in SSI tag <!--#include virtual="name" -->
    does not begin with a slash (/) then it is taken from directory of
    the curent document.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Fri, 19 Nov 1999 00:00:00 +0300

smallsrv (1.205) unstable; urgency=low

  * Any CGI file extension can be associated with a specified
    application or DLL.
  * Protocol output has been optimized.
  * Setup prompt.

 -- Maksim Feoktistov <max@smallsrv.com>  Fri, 12 Nov 1999 00:00:00 +0300

